// 03.11 Do While Loops

// very similar to a While Loop but While can have ZERO executions if the condition fails
// Do While will have AT LEAST one execution of the loop.


// start with Do keyword
// then create code block
// at the end of the code block we type while followed by our loop condition

do {

} while (loop condition)


